%% Trace: features/04-解除綁定Email.feature + 05-解除綁定手機.feature
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant Ctrl as AccountContactController
    participant Auth as JwtAuthGuard
    participant Svc as ContactUnbindService
    participant Repo as MemberAuthRepository
    participant CRM as CrmCustomerGateway

    Note over User,FE: 使用者已登入且已綁定 Email + 手機（BR-47 前提）
    User->>FE: 帳號設定 → 點擊「解除綁定 Email/手機」
    FE-->>User: 顯示二次確認彈窗 (BR-48 v1.7 不需密碼)
    User->>FE: 確認
    FE->>Ctrl: DELETE /account/bindings/email 或 /mobile [Bearer]
    Ctrl->>Auth: validateJwt
    Ctrl->>Svc: unbind(currentUserId, channel)
    Svc->>Repo: findById(currentUserId)
    Repo-->>Svc: member_auth
    Svc->>Svc: assertBothBound(member_auth) - BR-47
    Svc->>Repo: UPDATE member_auths SET email=null OR mobile_phone=null (依 channel)
    Svc->>CRM: clearCustomerEmailOrMobile(customer_id, channel)
    Svc-->>Ctrl: unbound
    Ctrl-->>FE: 204 No Content
    FE-->>User: 該聯絡方式改為「綁定」按鈕；另一種仍可登入
